651
00:39:49,780 --> 00:39:51,349
Datanglah ke Laputa setelah les.

652
00:39:59,889 --> 00:40:00,959
Ada apa?

653
00:40:04,630 --> 00:40:06,229
Kamu mau datang ke rumahku?

654
00:40:06,700 --> 00:40:07,970
Rumahmu?

655
00:40:08,530 --> 00:40:09,599
Ya.

656
00:40:10,169 --> 00:40:11,999
Kamu tidak pernah ke rumahku.

657
00:40:31,119 --> 00:40:33,030
