- Hei, kamu sudah pulang.

658
00:40:33,930 --> 00:40:36,599
Hei, Young Chul.

659
00:40:37,430 --> 00:40:38,559
Halo.

660
00:40:39,570 --> 00:40:40,599
Hai.

661
00:40:41,999 --> 00:40:43,900
Kami ingin di sini dan pergi bersama ke tempat les.

662
00:40:44,240 --> 00:40:46,169
